# AI Ops Entry Flow for Claude

Use the copied framework docs as the source of truth.

## Required Flow

1. Run `G0`.
2. Recommend one process plus one or two alternatives.
3. Wait for explicit user selection.
4. Record the selected process with `python3 scripts/set_process_context.py --process <PROCESS> --wp <WP-ID> --team-mode auto`.
5. Resolve `team` vs `single` before implementation on team-capable processes.
6. Use `{{ wp_path }}` and `{{ changelog_path }}` for process records.
